This paper deals with the problem of inferring data sharing relationships between advertisers and trackers in the online advertising ecosystem. This involves analyzing the bidding behavior of advertisers and studying the presence of trackers. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
